{"tid":766713,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"殺死咗會流出黃色汁液出嚟嘅昆蟲","createTime":"2018-08-03T21:43:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T12:42:32.000Z","uid":49274,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e9335aa278d83168be3a92e0e55c2ccc4b3a4d54","tid":766713,"uid":49274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T21:43:25.000Z","msg":"話說我岩岩打算瞓教，隻右手好似俾嘢撩緊咁，我以為係頭髮所以用力一捉，聽到清脆嘅碎殼聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後心知不妙就沖出廳一野fing我隻手隻野落枱，咁岩屋企人起咗身幫我沖左落馬桶，所以我影唔切相。<br />\n佢話係兒時玩開嘅昆蟲，佢地叫臭屁蟲(但又唔係會痾14粒蛋果種) 係會痾啲好&quot;押&quot;嘅尿出嚟果隻。<br />\n而我依家鏈碎咗隻昆蟲嘅手指啲黃色液體洗唔甩，好似黃色螢光筆highlight果隻色，我洗極手點卒都卒唔甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到底咩蟲嚟架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  屋企人又唔知學名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b680a3bfacc40ddfa846d321ec4488059a7dec3","tid":766713,"uid":49274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T21:50:06.000Z","msg":"唉 心理作用定點，隻手好痹又好&quot;拿&quot; <br />\n我搵咗一次張被同全張床都無同伴"},{"pid":"55bb74ee3f3261fcba915a8fbbf3664d927856c3","tid":766713,"uid":176472,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T21:51:43.000Z","msg":"無人理鳩你就好訓啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d34fb5edeab992b5afaaa2bdfe0e98f43c3021a","tid":766713,"uid":87428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T21:57:26.000Z","msg":"切得 聽日起身必見壞疽"},{"pid":"274b7ac3649b75a184bf06689fb75580071d3395","tid":766713,"uid":49274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T22:04:30.000Z","msg":"說好嘅學術台呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd082981a58b71edf09b1456ffc20611d98afb06","tid":766713,"uid":2643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T22:05:20.000Z","msg":"下世小心啲"},{"pid":"98cc3affa3c0457da7614e1915a5378e45769ab1","tid":766713,"uid":101587,"like":0,"